NOTE:

A: addition of a file
D: deletion of a file
U: file is unmerged (you must complete the merge before it can be committed)
C: copy of a file into a new one
M: modification of the contents or mode of a file
R: renaming of a file
T: change in the type of the file
X: "unknown" change type (most probably a bug, please report it)

tips:

WSZYSTKO PONIZEJ, jest mega ważne, rekruter do pracy bedzie patrzyl czy korzystasz z tab complition, albo jakie masz commity w repo.

1. tab complition
2. ctrl + strzaleczki
3. alt + mouse1 , kursosryrryry kilka
4. alt + mouse1 => cursor w konsoli
5. ctrl + 'w' kasuje slowa w konsoli
6. Use source control (diff's)
7. Commity: start with verb ;-), albo /first-app (sciezka):
   commits examples:
   food-app: initial commit //
   food-app/public: replace favicon.ico

